Cheryl L. SICKLER, Petitioner, v. DEPARTMENT OF VETERANS AFFAIRS, Respondent. No. 05-3353. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. July 12, 2006. Rehearing Denied Sept. 15, 2006.

Before MICHEL, Chief Judge, FRIEDMAN, Senior Circuit Judge and MAYER, Circuit Judge.

Judgment

PER CURIAM:

This CAUSE having been heard and considered, it is ORDERED and ADJUDGED:

AFFIRMED. See Fed. Cir. R. 36.
